<font color="#FF0000">STRANGE TRIP</font><br>
<tt>Tue Nov 26 19:52:47 US/Eastern 1996
</tt><p>
I turned 18 on a boat bound for French-Indo China. The date was October 18,1965. I spent 2 years of my youth and 35 years of adulthood trying to come to grips with that experience. What comes to mind is a song that has a refrain about what a long strange trip it's been. 
